## Risk Categories Reference
<!-- Use these standard categories when classifying risks: -->
- **Technical** — architecture, infrastructure, data, integration
- **AI/ML** — model quality, data quality, bias, drift, explainability
- **Commercial** — budget, timeline, ROI, market
- **Regulatory** — compliance, GDPR, AI Act, data sovereignty
- **Organisational** — skills, stakeholder, change management
- **Operational** — deployment, support, monitoring, SLA
- **External** — vendor, dependency, market conditions

